<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='438000' id='t-438000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440000' id='t-440000'>So what would some of the specific challenges</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>look like?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445000' id='t-445000'>I would say, on the top of the agenda</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='448000' id='t-448000'>is sex trafficking.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450000' id='t-450000'>And I'll just say two things about this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='452000' id='t-452000'>The slavery at the peak of the slave trade</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455000' id='t-455000'>in the 1780s:</span>
