<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676000' id='t-676000'>With economic opportunity,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678000' id='t-678000'>it can be transformative.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680000' id='t-680000'>Let me tell you about Saima.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682000' id='t-682000'>She lives in a small village outside Lahore, Pakistan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686000' id='t-686000'>And at the time, she was miserable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>She was beaten every single day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>by her husband, who was unemployed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692000' id='t-692000'>He was kind of a gambler type -- and unemployable, therefore --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>and took his frustrations out on her.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>Well, when she had her second daughter,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699000' id='t-699000'>her mother in-law told her son,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>&quot;I think you'd better get a second wife.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>Saima's not going to produce you a son.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>This is when she had her second daughter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>At the time, there was</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>a microlending group in the village</span>
