<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717000' id='t-717000'>Saima took that money,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>and she started an embroidery business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='723000' id='t-723000'>The merchants liked her embroidery; it sold very well,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725000' id='t-725000'>and they kept asking for more.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727000' id='t-727000'>And when she couldn't produce enough,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729000' id='t-729000'>she hired other women in the village.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>Pretty soon she had 30 women in the village</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='734000' id='t-734000'>working for her embroidery business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736000' id='t-736000'>And then,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>when she had to transport all of the embroidery goods</span>
